your daughter, then...

1010
01:00:46,043 --> 01:00:48,043
No, Frankie.

1011
01:00:48,045 --> 01:00:51,313
Do you know how schools
like Wesleyan work?

1012
01:00:51,315 --> 01:00:54,116
