to offer athletic scholarships?

1014
01:00:58,088 --> 01:00:59,988
No.

1015
01:00:59,990 --> 01:01:03,225
Athletic directors tend
to work around issues like these

1016
01:01:03,227 --> 01:01:05,127
by helping their athletes

1017
